snippet.title: Rogue Invader Trailer 1
snippet.description:
The first official trailer for Rogue Invader, 1-Bit Rogue-Lite Action Shooter. Gear up and get ready to drop, because YOU are the invader. Releasing Feb 2021 for PC/Mac.

Official Website: http://rogueinvader.com/
